#: lib/retro_hex_chat/commands/handlers/ns.ex:85
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Register and protect your nickname with a password through NickServ.\n"
"Subcommands: register <password>, identify <password>, ghost <nick> <password>, info [nick], drop <password>, help.\n"
"Register: claims current nickname. Identify: authenticates each session.\n"
"Ghost: disconnects a stale session using the registered nickname's password."
msgstr ""
"通過 NickServer 用密碼註冊並保護您的暱稱 。\n"
"子命令: 註冊 <ph0></ph0>, 識別 <ph1></ph1>, 鬼魂 <ph2></ph2>> <ph3></ph3>, 信息[nick], 放下 <ph4></ph4>, 幫助.\n"
"註冊:聲稱目前暱稱。 識別:認證每個會話。\n"
"Ghost:使用註冊暱稱的密碼斷開僵硬會話."

